   <div class="row"> 
    <h1 class="small-12 small-text-center columns fourOhFourPageMissing">404 PAGE MISSING</h1> 
   </div> 
   <div class="row"> 
    <h2 class="small-12 large-8 small-text-center small-centered columns fourOhFourHeading">LOOKS LIKE YOUR PAGE WASN'T FOUND.</h2> 
   </div> 
   <div class="row"> 
    <p class="small-12 large-7 small-text-center small-centered columns introText">You may have typed the address incorrectly or the page may not exist. In the meantime you can <br class="show-for-large-up"><span class="white">play some music on the Elliott Tower’s bells.</span></p> 
   </div> 
  </div> 
  <div tabindex="0" id="learnASongButton"> 



<img tabindex="0" id="learnASongGraphic" src="/media/Oakland/Assets/404/images/musicNote.png" width="23" height="23" alt="Learn a new Song">
   <span tabindex="0" id="learnASongText">LEARN A SONG</span> 
  </div> 
  <div id="learnASongContainer"> 
   <h3>Learn to Play</h3> 
   <div class="song" data-lyric-set-number="0"> 
    <p class="songTitle">"Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star"</p> 
    <hr class="learnToPlayHR"> 
    <p class="songLyrics">Twinkle • Twinkle • Little • Star</p> 
    <p class="songNotes">CC • GG • AA • G</p> 
    <p class="songLyrics">How I • wonder • what you • are</p> 
    <p class="songNotes">FF • EE • DD • C</p> 
   </div> 
   <div class="song" data-lyric-set-number="1"> 
    <p class="songTitle">"Mary Had A Little Lamb"</p> 
    <hr class="learnToPlayHR"> 
    <p class="songLyrics">Mary • had a • Little • Lamb</p> 
    <p class="songNotes">ED • CD • EE • E</p> 
    <p class="songLyrics">His • fleece • was white • as snow</p> 
    <p class="songNotes">E • D • DE • DC</p> 
   </div> 
   <div id="newSongContainer"> 
    <div id="newSong"> 
     <img src="/media/Oakland/Assets/404/images/musicNote.png" alt="Music note" tabindex="0" id="newSongGraphic" height="23" width="23">
     <span tabindex="0" id="newSongText">NEW SONG</span> 
    </div> 
    <div id="closeLearnASong"> 
<img src="/media/Oakland/Assets/404/images/closeX.png" alt="X - closes Learn to Play window" tabindex="0" width="18" height="18" id="newSongGraphic">
